### 🚀 Testing in Remix IDE
1. Open [Remix IDE](https://remix.ethereum.org).  
2. Paste the contract code into a new file (e.g., `EtherSplitter.sol`).  
3. Compile with Solidity ^0.8.0.  
4. Deploy the contract — provide an array of addresses in the constructor (e.g., `[0x123..., 0x456...]`).  
5. Call `distribute()` and send Ether with the transaction.  
6. Check balances of recipient accounts — each should receive an equal share.  
7. Use `getBalance()` to confirm if any remainder is left in the contract.  
